CMD 1:
$docker run mysql

$docker docker run -e MYSQL_ROOT_PASSWORD="root" -d mysql

$docker container list
  Note NAME of recent(topmost) container
$docker inspect <name noted in previous command>
  Note IP Address


CMD 2:
$docker run -it mysql /bin/bash
In bash:
 >mysql -h <IPAddress> -u root -p
 >Type password(here its "root")
 >show databases;
 
